room_title: Escape room "The Naughty List" by Southern Escape Room in Monroe (LA)
room_description: You have a sneaking suspicion that you’ve been put on Santa’s Naughty List. Santa, Mrs Claus and the Elves will be on break for exactly 1 hour before getting back to Santa’s Workshop. This should give you plenty of time to find your way through the mysteries of Santa’s shop, find the Naughty List and remove your name before they return.
